## ‚úÖ UPDATE PROTOCOL

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Task as Task Entry
    participant Track1 as Track 1
    participant Track2 as Track 2
    participant Track3 as Track 3
    participant Integration as Integration
    participant History as State History
    
    Task->>Track1: Initialize Track
    Task->>Track2: Initialize Track
    Task->>Track3: Initialize Track
    
    par Track 1 Execution
        Track1->>Track1: Update Progress
        Track1->>History: Record State
        Track1->>Track1: Check Rollback
        alt Need Rollback
            Track1->>History: Record Rollback
            History->>Track1: Restore State
        end
    and Track 2 Execution
        Track2->>Track2: Update Progress
        Track2->>History: Record State
        Track2->>Track2: Check Rollback
        alt Need Rollback
            Track2->>History: Record Rollback
            History->>Track2: Restore State
        end
    and Track 3 Execution
        Track3->>Track3: Update Progress
        Track3->>History: Record State
        Track3->>Track3: Check Rollback
        alt Need Rollback
            Track3->>History: Record Rollback
            History->>Track3: Restore State
        end
    end
    
    Track1->>Integration: Ready for Integration
    Track2->>Integration: Ready for Integration
    Track3->>Integration: Ready for Integration
    
    Integration->>Integration: Verify Integration
    alt Integration Failed
        Integration->>Track1: Rollback Required
        Integration->>Track2: Rollback Required
        Integration->>Track3: Rollback Required
    else Integration Successful
        Integration->>Task: Update Status
        Integration->>History: Record Integration
        Task->>Task: Check Completion
    end
```

